OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy but dry at first then
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain at times from mid-
OL,7,Fmorning. The day will be mild with
OL,8,Ffreshening southerly winds along the
OL,9,Feast coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with patchy light rain
OL,12,Fin the evening. The rain becomes heavy
OL,13,Faway from the coasts from late
OL,14,Fevening. A mild and windy night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Fbecoming dry from late morning with
OL,18,Fincreasing sunny spells during the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
